- Enumerated six unverified assumptions the implementer/reviewer MUST verify: the PyYAML `on:`â†’`True` quirk (assumed, not tested â€” needs a dedicated fixture test); `bump_version.py --dry-run` verified only by grepping its argparse (line ~302), never executed; `yamllint` living in the lint pixi env (may need `pixi run --environment lint yamllint`); action SHA pins copied from sibling jobs without re-verifying against upstream release tags; brittle string-containment `if:` matching (a semantically equivalent `github.ref_type == 'tag'` rewrite fails the guard â€” intentional, but failure messages must say update guard + workflow together); line numbers cited from origin/main while the checkout sat on a stale feature branch.
